• 26.02.RS - $1,750 – Burnaby Female Ice Hockey Association for the U-18 A1 Team to attend 2026 Provincial Championships in Trail, BC; and
• 26.03.RS - $1,500 – Renbu Dojo Kendo Club for the 2026 Canadian National Junior Kendo Championships in Burlington, Ontario.
